    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "That's not what I meant. You don't differ the whole rendering but only part of it (the image). By that I mean setting the src attribute of the img tag while still updating instantaneous part (like title, tags or whatever). This is a very special use case, hence it should be a special widget not an option.\n\nOf course if you differ the whole rendering, it produce a similarly weird effect.\n",
